{"tid":763116,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"墨西哥客機墜毀37傷機師傷勢最重","createTime":"2018-08-01T00:56:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-01T03:06:04.000Z","uid":14208,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e0d8c9abd014788fe17a74e5d17c0658fabbc627","tid":763116,"uid":14208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T00:56:07.000Z","msg":"墨西哥發生墜機意外，墨西哥航空一架客機，原定由北部杜蘭戈州，飛往首都墨西哥城，但起飛後5分鐘，就在機場10公里外墜毀。客機載有97名乘客及4名機員，杜蘭戈州州長表示，無人死亡，民防部門表示只有37人輕傷，由於機頭先著地，機師傷勢最重。事發後大批救援人員到場將傷者送院。機場管理公司表示，初步報告懷疑是惡劣天氣，導致墜機。<br />\n<br />\n出事客機由巴西製造，最高可載100名乘客。客機失事後殘骸起火冒出濃煙，機體尚算完整，但機頂嚴重損毀。多名乘客逃生後走到公路尋求協助。有目擊者表示墜機前聽到巨響。總統培尼亞指示國防、民防及運輸等多個部門全力應對。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_367&amp;itemid=1022162\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3Fcsid%3D261_367%26itemid%3D1022162&d=j7yiGoP44mDpAHwzKZze2%2FjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=5b61ed09\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_367&amp;itemid=1022162</a><br />\n<br />\n真係冇人死咁堅?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b7fe7ab3549537011b02763f1c81d3f1b9be1cc","tid":763116,"uid":14208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T00:58:29.000Z","msg":"墨西哥航空班機墜毀！現場濃煙密布　無人死亡85傷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imagelab.nownews.com/?w=1080&amp;q=85&amp;src=https://rssimg.nownews.com/images/5b60e80549e7bf4adb9695de_201808010651.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimagelab.nownews.com%2F%3Fw%3D1080%26q%3D85%26src%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Frssimg.nownews.com%2Fimages%2F5b60e80549e7bf4adb9695de_201808010651.jpg&h=366feb51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲墨西哥航空一架飛機墜毀在田野之中。（圖／翻攝自Alex Macheras推特）<br />\n<br />\n墨西哥航空（ Aeromexico ）一架編號 AM2431 班機，在當地時間 31 日下午 3 時左右墜毀在墨西哥杜蘭戈州，機上共載有 97 名乘客與 4 名機組員。最新消息指出，事故造成 85 人受傷，無人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，這架班機原先預定從杜蘭戈市起飛前往墨西哥市。有報導指出，飛機是在緊急降落時墜毀；但也有其他說法指出，飛機在起飛後不到 5 分鐘就墜毀。而墨西哥航空已經確認這起事故為「意外事件」，詳細的墜機原因還在調查中。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.nownews.com/nownews_production/images/5b60e8055a2b384b1927216f_201808010651.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.nownews.com%2Fnownews_production%2Fimages%2F5b60e8055a2b384b1927216f_201808010651.jpg&h=4b24a483&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲消防與醫護人員都已趕往現場救援。（圖／翻攝自Alex Macheras推特）<br />\n<br />\n杜蘭戈州長托雷斯（ Jos&eacute; Rosas Aispuro ）在推特上指出，事故地點發生在該州的瓜達盧佩維多利亞將軍國際機場（ General Guadalupe Victoria International Airport ）附近，事故的相關細節之後會陸續公布。最新消息指出，這起事故造成 85 人受傷，無人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nownews.com/news/20180801/2795323\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fnews%2F20180801%2F2795323&d=j7yiGoP44mDpAHwzKZze2%2FjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=aa753cd6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nownews.com/news/20180801/2795323</a>"},{"pid":"4cfd0ec17934eacb07b4438d01b5a975d30959b4","tid":763116,"uid":53524,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T00:59:55.000Z","msg":"客機墜毀 無人死亡"},{"pid":"05b1876f42d0f25503b53045d762000bc458bb89","tid":763116,"uid":39012,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T01:13:44.000Z","msg":"今次之後空難存活率升左幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7e1ef6a5e1d781825ff634612c2371abe83e9d8","tid":763116,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T01:18:37.000Z","msg":"比個機師like先"},{"pid":"998da53ad278d375e00908cbf4b4266fc8caa731","tid":763116,"uid":2923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T01:19:33.000Z","msg":"會唔會又拍做電影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b67a451455efe164912c703f558f339171d4918","tid":763116,"uid":23087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T01:23:23.000Z","msg":"哇 咁都無人死"},{"pid":"638e376e9084b612e0b4213e0438d16259c8b075","tid":763116,"uid":16343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"998da53ad278d375e